mod_metadata.title: Bound Hearts
mod_metadata.author: TruthSeeker
mod_metadata.description: A custom music pack for KH2 Refined. Ost picks are from a Fire Emblem rom hack called Bound Destiny. Full Playlist of music on Youtube. Playlist called Bound Hearts by TruthSeeker64.

game_metadata.name: Bound Hearts
game_metadata.description: Blaze Beyond Dusk, Fight On for a new Destiny. Bound Hearts Music Pack.
